"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-paris-2024-firm-anti-sex-beds-leave-olympic-athletes-stiff\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Matt Hardy  Deputy Sports Editor - City AM  The so-called anti-sex cardboard beds at theParis 2024 OlympicVillage have left athletes stiff with firm mattresses causing discomfort.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian water polo player Tilly Kearns said on social media: \\\"This is how night one went on the cardboard beds.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\", \"score\": 0.9999997772513572, \"rank\": 2.1856009552937266e-07, \"text\": \"Kearns\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's actually rock solid.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can flip them over apparently to a softer side but this was the softer side!\\\"\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She then goes on to talk further while her roommate can be heard saying: \\\"My back is about to fall off\\\".\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The beds are made of three modules, supposedly allowing athletes to choose the firmness of their mattress.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The thin duvets sit on sustainable beds which are made in France and will be fully recycled after the games.\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": [